
  <h1>The RavenRidge Blog</h1>

  <p>If you recall, there are four of us here at RavenRidge Family Farm. Four opinionated, cbd-using, forest loving folks.</p>
  <p>As you likely know, we make cbd products. We also grow our hemp following regenerative practices. You'll find information on these things and more in the blog posts below (scroll to the end for the full archive).</p>
  {{#each content.posts_by_category}}
  <section>
    <h2>{{title}}</h2>
    <div class='flex_box post_list'>
      {{#each posts}}
        {{#if featuredImage}}
          <a href='/blog/{{slug}}'><img src='{{featuredImage}}'/>{{title}}</a>
        {{/if}}
      {{/each}}
    </div>
  </section>
  {{/each}}
  <section>
    <h2>Full Blog Archive</h2>
    <ul>
    {{#each content.posts}}
      <li><a href='/blog/{{slug}}'>{{title}}</a></li>
    {{/each}}
    </ul>
  </section>
